"(1) (i) A dense, sulfurous haze blanketed the landscape as the sky above darkened with an unnatural crimson glow. Zoe, a local resident returning home after a morning walk, felt the ground tremble beneath her feet just as the first low rumble rolled across the valley. Trees swayed violently, and the air thickened with the acrid scent of ash, transforming the familiar path into a shifting, dangerous expanse.\n(2) (i) By midday on , the ground erupted in a sudden, deafening roar. Lava fountains spewed from a fissure in the earth, casting rivers of molten rock across the fields and sending plumes of smoke spiraling into the sky. The once tranquil village now vibrated with the raw power of nature, and Zoe, caught in the open, could only watch as the landscape was irrevocably changed before her eyes. Kampong Cham Province. March 23, 2024.\n(3) (i) , witnessing the relentless fury of the volcanic eruption, stood frozen in terror as the sky cracked open and the earth roared. Her breath came in sharp gasps, the heat of the ash stinging her face, while the ground beneath her boots gave way to trembling, glowing rock. In that single, chaotic day in , she bore silent witness to the unstoppable force of the volcano. Zoe Brown. witnessed a volcanic eruption."